::DeathScythe/Shredder::

DeathScythe dives under the rockets heading for him. He swears under his 
breath. This was not good. He keeps flying continuing to head north.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder looks at the Cybertronian Fire from a distance. He growls, opening a 
channel to Bobertron. "So let me get this straight," he says, "We're supposed 
to help the Maximals here?"
